      "raw_text": "At its meeting yesterday the\nWoman's club voted to stand\nby Mrs. Stafford and the COM\nmittee on police matrons and\nremain In the fight to finish\n\n\nInstead of discord, as some\nnewspapers had intimated, the\nutmost harmony prevailed and\nthe club members present were\nin the best Of spirits."
